link_metadata.description: I dreamed of moving abroad and got my chance when I was accepted to Trinity College. I enjoyed my studies, but Ireland wasn't what I expected.
link_metadata.title: I thought my life would change when I moved to Ireland. Unfortunately, I never felt I belonged, and I moved home a year later.
